== Description == You were a construction worker on planet mars in the nuclear waste section of the base when a power outage knocked out the power. You begin to hear strange noises while ou try to fix the lighting problem. Soon after you get some of the lights up and running so you head back to the main part of base. Along the way you find a few surprises waiting for you.
